## Quick Revision Points
- Roles span SOC Analyst, Pentester, Network Security Engineer, Red/Blue Teamer, Vulnerability Analyst, Cloud/IoT Security Specialist.
- Certification path: Network+/Security+ (foundational) → CEH/CCNA (intermediate) → OSCP/GPEN/CISSP (advanced/specialized).
- Employers value hands-on demonstrated skill (projects, CTFs) as much as or more than certifications alone.
- Career progression often starts in general IT/networking before specializing into security.
- Legal authorization and continuous learning are non-negotiable industry requirements, not optional extras.
